    This is a fruit cognitive sticker game designed for children, including more than 100 kinds of fruits, including berries, citrus, drupe, pome, melons, and is equipped with 2 languages: English pronunciation, Chinese, children can learn in the course of the game is very good and remember these fruits help your baby, through visual, auditory and tactile perception of the full range of the world.
There are basically all the fruits in life:
Strawberry, blueberry, raspberry, blackberry, mulberry, grape, green, red, crystal grape;
Sugar orange, kumquat, orange, orange, grapefruit, grapefruit, lemon, grapefruit, pomelo;
Peach, plum, cherry, apricot, plum, red bayberry, prunes, plum, red dates, dates, dates, olives, litchi, longan, areca (Gui Yuan);
Apple, pear, red delicious, crabapple, Shaguo, persimmon, mangosteen, plum, loquat, carambola, hawthorn, Cherry Tomatoes, figs, ginkgo, mangosteen, pitaya, kiwi;
Muskmelon, watermelon, muskmelon, melon, papaya, melon;
Pineapple, mango, coconut, chestnut, kiwi fruit, guava, durian, banana, sugarcane, pomegranate, lotus seed, walnut
